Oke, makanlah 'rabri-jalebi'
setelah membeli saree hari ini.

00:16:34.623 --> 00:16:36.183
Benar-benar?  - Ya.

00:16:36.503 --> 00:16:40.943
Ayo pergi sebelum
bunglon berubah warna.

00:16:41.103 --> 00:16:43.103
Bergerak cepat.

00:16:48.263 --> 00:16:49.343
Ibu.

00:16:53.703 --> 00:16:54.783
Dahi.

00:16:55.823 --> 00:16:57.583
Kesehatan Anda tampaknya baik-baik saja.

